# Personal / machine-local state — not shared across the team. These
# files were being picked up by `git add -A` and nearly landed in a
# commit by mistake; keep the pattern list tight so `git status` stays
# readable but new personal files in the same categories don't leak.
.env-personal
hive-personal.yaml
agents-personal/
mokie-*.png
.playwright-mcp/
test-results/
.mcp.json
